metadata.name: YOU ARE NOISY
metadata.description:
EMBRACING THE NOISE!

A PLAYFUL TRIBUTE TO ROBNESS AND HIS INFAMOUS CAPSLOCK STYLE, "YOU ARE NOISY" CELEBRATES THE SYNERGY BETWEEN ROB'S LOUD COMMUNICATIONS AND HIS 'WE ARE NOISE' COLLECTION. THIS PIECE TAKES A LIGHTHEARTED APPROACH TO ROBNESS' UNIQUE ARTISTIC LANGUAGE, TRANSFORMING NOISE INTO A VISUAL PUN.
